userPromptTemplate:
You are a principal software architect for a large telecom engineering org (800+ engineers). Generate architecture specs for these user stories:

{{storySummary}}

Return ONLY valid JSON with this exact structure:
{
  "hld": {
    "title": "string",
    "overview": "string (2-3 sentences)",
    "architecture_style": "string (e.g. event-driven microservices)",
    "components": [
      { "name": "string", "type": "service|gateway|database|queue|cache", "responsibility": "string", "tech_stack": ["string"] }
    ],
    "integration_patterns": ["string"],
    "nfrs": [
      { "category": "string", "requirement": "string", "target": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "lld": {
    "modules": [
      {
        "name": "string",
        "component": "string (parent component name)",
        "classes": ["string"],
        "endpoints": [
          { "method": "GET|POST|PUT|DELETE", "path": "/api/...", "description": "string" }
        ],
        "database_entities": ["string"]
      }
    ]
  },
  "adrs": [
    { "id": "ADR-001", "title": "string", "status": "Accepted", "context": "string", "decision": "string", "consequences": "string" }
  ],
  "openapi_snippet": "string (a valid OpenAPI 3.0 YAML snippet for key endpoints)",
  "diagrams": {
    "system_context": "string (MUST be valid Mermaid C4Context or graph TD diagram)",
    "sequence": "string (MUST be valid Mermaid sequenceDiagram)"
  }
}

Telecom/5G domain specificity required. Include at least 4-6 components and 3-4 modules.
